message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you the opportunity to purchase this valuable product. Given its unique features and benefits, I'm initially proposing a price of $25000. What are your thoughts?
Alice, I truly appreciate the features of your product, but I can only justify a purchase at a price of $10000. Can we make that work?
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $10000 is significantly below the value of this product. I'm willing to be flexible, so how about we meet in the middle at $20000?
